column10: dig_threshold_desc:I generally tried to stay above 50 gems
column11: or the bare minimum of 45. Tried using the strategy of If the second dig was 40 or under I would leave after  the first dig.
column14: If the gems were around 105+ I would sometimes dig again.
column17: It would be based on the two reasonings above. How many gems on first dig
column18: and how many gems on the second dig from the previous planet.
